{"tid":1661954,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Warning! 中共潮興用「洋五毛」抹黑手足!!","createTime":"2019-10-18T12:31:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-14T10:09:25.000Z","uid":293012,"like":49,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"d7ab658c6516c84fcf5f488a8436d88e0c7da03d","tid":1661954,"uid":293012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T12:31:44.000Z","msg":"迎排喺twitter同youtube多左唔少鬼佬現身說法，先唔理中共成撚日都話鬼佬點衰點衰，但又要用阻鬼佬去幫佢地講好說話咁撚戇鳩，話西方啲媒體好biased，要傳遞所謂嘅「真相」比全世界云云，但講個啲野全撚部都係五毛FAQ黎！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但大家千祈唔好比佢地嚇親，佢地通常都係幫中宣部做野，或者收受中共黑金嘅西方記者（幫中國做大外宣嘅外國記者人工高，甚至有套房！！），根本就係中共喉舌，呃啲唔知頭唔知路嘅鬼佬（同鄉更有說服力），麻煩大家見一個report一個！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">例子 （取至品蔥）</span></span><br />\n「這不是自由，這是暴亂、破壞、暴力。香港的暴徒僅僅因為你表達自己的觀點，就把你毆打流血，這不是自由。」<br />\n<br />\n「你知道希特勒也是&lsquo;民主&rsquo;選出來的嗎？」「你覺得只要能投票給任何人，就是取得了民主了是嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n「香港的暴徒就是在毀壞、無序、經濟重創，想與幫助自己實現繁榮的祖國分離，他們太荒謬了！」<br />\n<br />\n「我覺得香港警察非常溫柔了。講真，你用這樣的暴力，拿著鐵棍去打警察，你這樣不叫暴徒？」<br />\n<br />\n「你看美國的警察，或者其他國家的警察，遇到這樣的&lsquo;示威&rsquo;，我指像香港的&lsquo;示威&rsquo;，一定開了槍，多一千倍！&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">洋五毛圖鑑</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><ins>老牌洋五毛-Nathan Rich 火鍋大王</ins></strong><br />\n活躍於Youtube界，美國有案底，因為冇得撈被迫黎中國做五毛<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aSyTx2i.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaSyTx2i.png&h=d6c80a4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nDan Cohen <br />\n近排喺twitter成日retweet佢條「真相」片，條友係幫RT-Russia Today做野，RT係俄國黨媒，同人民日報、環球時報冇分別，獨裁政權梗係會幫獨裁政權啦！！<br />\n（條Carl Zha係支蛆黎，好撚多follower，可以順手report. ）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0xCUhuD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0xCUhuD.png&h=f8c54df4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nJaron Lines<br />\n呢隻唔使我多講啦，用「希特拉係民選出黎」呢一個混淆視聽嘅謬論黎詆毀民主，有巴打起左佢底：<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1652513/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1652513/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iz0OmZi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fiz0OmZi.png&h=d75bf298&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1jrxOC7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1jrxOC7.jpg&h=dcfd3834&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n鬼佬都要乞食，生於民主自由嘅國家，卻要詆毀民主自由，簡直係國恥<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n送佢去大灣區終生侍奉祖國啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbc9fae136a8e09133fff2c644d8729651bda157","tid":1661954,"uid":293012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T12:34:34.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推～"},{"pid":"806e08a69e89502a2b00adb6a21c4290fe1ded2d","tid":1661954,"uid":21139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T12:34:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1dee5aee03e4a3931d5739a662e5956fbc84c1da","tid":1661954,"uid":235374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T12:37:46.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"779d35ba30bfc373cc13d8bea9148c23fb02f011","tid":1661954,"uid":311198,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T12:38:52.000Z","msg":"其實咁樣係咪某程度上崇洋媚外 中共自己去做漢奸？"},{"pid":"3caa54e8bda89b96ba1d7833c01f3d01c029753d","tid":1661954,"uid":186882,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T12:39:02.000Z","msg":"果個火鍋大王就係專呃d中產又識d英文既藍屍<br />\n有見過一個本身幾有料既IT人share佢d片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e32d833dc2a948744035c0b1adae8053cd493f5","tid":1661954,"uid":331173,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T12:39:44.000Z","msg"